data.description:
Built in 2017, this up to date, move in ready house in coveted Falls Crossing Subdivision is a must see!  This home offers a charming open floor plan 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence that effortlessly combines comfort, style, and functionality. Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this inviting home is an ideal haven for families or those seeking a spacious and well-designed living space.
As you approach the property, you'll be greeted by a manicured front lawn, lots of landscaping, and a welcoming porch, setting the tone for the warmth that awaits inside. Step through the front door into a well-lit foyer, where natural light spills in, highlighting the tasteful neutral tones and modern finishes throughout.
The heart of the home is the open-concept living area, seamlessly connecting the living room, dining area, and kitchen. The living room features a cozy fireplace, perfect for chilly evenings, while large windows invite sunlight to fill the space. The adjacent dining area offers ample room for family gatherings or entertaining friends.
The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting stainless steel appliances, which stay with the house, granite countertops, and plenty of cabinet space. A convenient breakfast bar provides additional seating and serves as a central hub for socializing while preparing meals.
The master bedroom is a serene retreat, complete with an ensuite bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet. The two additional bedrooms are well-proportioned and share a stylishly appointed bathroom. Each bedroom features large windows, ensuring a bright and airy atmosphere.
Step outside to discover a private backyard, perfect for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply unwinding on a sunny day. The patio area is ideal for hosting BBQs or enjoying al fresco dining with family and friends.
Additional highlights of this home include a dedicated laundry room, ample storage space, and a two-car garage. The property is conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping centers, making it an excellent choice for those seeking both tranquility and accessibility.
Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect blend of comfort and style in this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem.
